<br>
That's the most complete, accurate, detailed and up to date listing of all spells available to the Magician class, as it's extracted directly from the spell data files.<br>
<br>
The only thing to be aware of is that many AAXP abilities will show up as level 1 spells.  These are normally pretty easy to identify, as they typically cost 0 mana (Servant of Ro costs 1 mana).  As all level 1 Magician spells are vendor purchased in your home town anyway, you shouldn't need this level 1 section of the listing. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
